{"id":1702,"date":"2024-08-26T19:35:35","date_gmt":"2024-08-26T19:35:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1702"},"modified":"2024-08-29T23:32:16","modified_gmt":"2024-08-29T23:32:16","slug":"lucarionite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/lucarionite\/","title":{"rendered":"Lucarionite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"big center text-large\">Lucarionite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Gift from the white-haired NPC in the Great Desert. The stone is a reward for completing the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-081\/\">\u201cWarmonger\u201d mission<\/a>, which requires you to win 2000 battles.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Lucario<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Gurun Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Gurun Town Pok\u00e9mon Center and head west to cross the bridge going out of the town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lucarionite\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-gurun-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Gurun Town Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Gurun Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue hugging the north edge of the desert island as you go west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lucarionite\/02-pokemon-unbound-following-the-northern-edge-of-the-island.jpg\" alt=\"Following the northern edge of the island. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the northern edge of the island.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually see a white-haired NPC with the side quest bubble on top of his head. Interact with him.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lucarionite\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-white-haired-npc.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the white-haired NPC. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the white-haired NPC.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This NPC gives you the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-081\/\">\u201cWarmonger\u201d<\/a> mission, and completing it rewards you with the Lucarionite mega stone.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lucarionite\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-description-for-the-warmonger-side-mission.jpg\" alt=\"The description for the \u201cWarmonger\u201d side mission. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The description for the \u201cWarmonger\u201d side mission.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1703,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1702","wiki","type-wiki","